intro.name: POINTMAN
intro.text: "♫ The prettiest girl I ever saw, was drinking bourbon through a straw."

intro.name: POINTMAN
intro.text: "♫ I placed my hand upon her knee, she said, "GI, you're teasing me.""

intro.name: POINTMAN
intro.text: "♫ I placed my hand upon her thigh, she said, "GI, that's way too high.""

intro.name: POINTMAN
intro.text: "♫ I picked her up, I laid her down, her long black hair lay all around."

intro.name: POINTMAN
intro.text: "♫ The wedding was a formal one, her daddy brought a white shotgun."

name: "Forever let us hold our banner high!"

intro.name: LEADER
intro.text: "♫ Who's the leader of the club that's made for you and me?"

intro.name: (ALL)
intro.text: "♫ M-I-C, K-E-Y, M-O-U-S-E."

intro.name: LEADER
intro.text: "♫ Who is marching coast to coast and far across the sea?"

intro.name: (ALL)
intro.text: "♫ M-I-C, K-E-Y, M-O-U-S-E."

intro.name: (ALL)
intro.text: "♫ Mickey Mouse!"

intro.name: LEADER (falsetto)
intro.text: "♫ Mickey Mouse!"

intro.name: POINTMAN
intro.text: "♫ I want a war, just like the war, that mutilated dear 'ole Dad."

intro.name: POINTMAN
intro.text: "♫ It was the one, and only war, that dear 'ole Daddy ever had."

intro.name: LEADER
intro.text: "Fucking lovely. Thanks POINTMAN."

intro.name: POINTMAN
intro.text: "Normally I warm up before a performance."

intro.name: OTHER1
intro.text: "♫ Ba ba ba, ba Barbara Ann"

intro.text: "♫ Ba ba ba, ba Barbara Ann"

intro.text: "♫ Barbara Aaaaaaannnnn"

intro.name: POINTMAN & OTHER2

intro.name: OTHER1
intro.text: "A hamburger. Fries - a hamburger with cheese - and a chocolate milkshake. From the diner on route 7."

intro.name: POINTMAN
intro.text: "What's it called?"

intro.name: OTHER1
intro.text: "I don't think it has a name."

intro.name: OTHER2
intro.text: "POINTMAN, why are you so quiet?"

intro.name: OTHER2
intro.text: "Come'on man, say something. Anything."
